# Implementation Plan - Modern Header Restructuring

The goal is to implement a new header layout for both the PDF generator (`corporatePdf.ts`) and the UI preview (`Requests.tsx`), precisely following the corporate standard shown in the reference image.

## Proposed Header Structure

The header will be organized into a balanced four-quadrant distribution with a secondary bottom border.

### 1. Top Section (Aligned at Y=10mm)
*   **Top Left**: Company Logo (AlanDick)
*   **Top Right**: 
    *   **Document Title**: "LEAVE APPLICATION FORM" (Bold Navy Blue, 20-24pt)
    *   **Metadata**: "No: [DocRef] | Date: [Date]" (Small Grey text, right-aligned)

### 2. Bottom Section (Starting below the Logo)
*   **Bottom Left**:
    *   **Corporate Identity**: "AlanDick East Africa Ltd." (Bold Black)
    *   **Address/Contact**: P.O Box info and Tel/Email (Normal Grey font)
*   **Horizontal Separator**: High-contrast Navy Blue horizontal line (1mm thickness) at the base of the entire header section.

